title: Papa datte, Shitai
synopsis: Asumi Kouya is a college student who wants to earn some extra money. Utilizing his talents for cooking and cleaning, he accepts a part-time job as a housekeeper. His employer is single father Keiichi Naruse, an attractive young man with a troubling history regarding his former staff.
staff: [['Noshitani, Mitsutaka', ['Director']], ['Enomoto, Takahiro', ['Sound Director']], ['Terashima, Junta', ['Theme Song Performance']], ['Yamanaka, Masahiro', ['Theme Song Performance']]]
